    <div class="wrapper">
        <h2>Web and Programming</h2>
        <p>I'm a programmer, web designer and developer, and occasional game maker. I have demonstrated expertise in <strong>Javascript</strong>, <strong>HTML</strong>, and hand-crafted <strong>CSS</strong>, and I also have extensive experience in PHP, SQL, C++, Perl, and Actionscript 3.</p>
        <div class="half left">
            <div class="padding">
                <p>I made the <a href="http://www.davepagurek.com/programming/xcalc-js/">XCalc.js Javascript library</a>, a computer algebra system which can parse, simplify, evaluate, differentiate, and graph mathematical expressions. Made with HTML, CSS and Javascript.</p>
                <p align="center"><a class="button small" href="http://www.davepagurek.com/programming/xcalc-js/">View Documentation and Demo</a></p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="half right">
