            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="half left">
            <div class="padding">
                <p>My website runs on <a href="http://davepagurek.com/programming/trestle">Trestle</a>, a lightweight Perl content management system featuring caching, templating, and an admin interface.</p>
                <p align="center"><a class="button small" href="http://davepagurek.com/programming/trestle">View Trestle Documentation</a></p>
